Justifications: Requirements listed below are implemented in source code for BAPHandlers SWC's which are using BAPHandler_PSO_ImExport library. Relevant requirement tags can be found e.g. in source code of: BAPHandler_Doorlocking, BAPHandler_IL2 (InteriorLight) or BAPHandler_Mirror SWC's. SWR_L3_CRoute_PSO_AP_464 SWR_L3_CRoute_PSO_AP_446 SWR_L3_CRoute_PSO_AP_452 SWR_L3_CRoute_PSO_AP_335 SWR_L3_CRoute_PSO_AP_463 SWR_L3_CRoute_PSO_AP_590 Corresponding software unit tests were prepared for relevant BAPHandler SWC units.
Requirements listed below are implemented by preparing relevant configuration. SWR_L3_CRoute_PSO_AP_698 SWR_L3_CRoute_PSO_AP_737 Because of this they cannot be reflected in the code by relevant requirement tags. The verification is done on system level, that's why no software unit tests were prepared to verify them.
